title: Gov. Andrew Cuomo | Trump and Fox Try to Distract from Coronavirus with "Obamagate": A Closer Look
description:
Seth takes a closer look at the president reeling politically from his deadly incompetence during the coronavirus pandemic.

Then, he talks to Governor Andrew Cuomo about how New York is approaching the pandemic.
